# Flaskion

Flaskion is a lightweight **MVC micro-framework** for Flask, providing developers with a **structured foundation** for scalable, maintainable applications. Inspired by Laravel, Flaskion introduces clean architecture, modular scaffolding, and a developer-first CLI to streamline your Flask workflow.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

âœ… **MVC Architecture** â€“ Clean separation of `controllers`, `models`, and `templates`  
âœ… **Built-in CLI** â€“ Scaffold full resources, controllers, models, and authentication with ease  
âœ… **Web & API Routing** â€“ Clean route structure split between HTML and JSON endpoints  
âœ… **DB Choice at Setup** â€“ Use SQLite, MySQL, or Postgres with built-in `.env` generation  
âœ… **Flask-Migrate Ready** â€“ Migrations are set up and ready to run on first build  
âœ… **Authentication Scaffolding** â€“ Generate full auth (login/register/logout/dashboard) with one command  

